Secondly, I am friends with many of the members of ADD. Until now I'd never had a problem with ADD. In fact I've even helped you on some raids without expecting anything in return. For example, at the request of Blal, I came and dropped a manaburn Talendor last week when you were having trouble and declined to roll on any loot because I knew your guilded needed it more than I. However, I do have a problem with the way this incident went down. The actions taken by ADD with reguard to the shissar were at best, very questionable.<br>
<br>
Ya, I'm a member of vis, but unlike what some of you might have heard, we respect the right of any guild/group not named wraith to have first dibs on a mob if they are in or clearly gathering in a zone before us with a sufficient force. Doesn't matter if they are just starting to work their way to a mob. For example, on 4-11-02, Vis was planning on taking the burrower parasite but lotus cult started gathering in the deep before we did. Sure, they only had a small force there at the time, but we respected the fact that they had started to gather in force first and had enough members online and otw to kill the worm. Clearly in this situation with ADD and radiant, reguardless of who's tracking bitch was in the zone first or who tried to stall who, Radiant was gathering at fear and went into fear before ADD. It is also clear that Radiant had a sufficient force to complete their task. Therefor, ADD should have respected this and never even zoned into PoF. At the very least ADD should have allowed Radiant to at least attempt the shissar since they were the first guild to enter.<br>
<br>
I'll give you the benifit of the doubt and allow for the fact that there was possibly some miscommunication between Radiant and ADD. Hindsight is 20/20 and all the facts may not have been clear to both guilds in the heat of the moment. Please try to refrain from getting yourselves into situations such as this ADD. It reflects poorly on your guild and unfortunately, a lot of people here are not nearly as forgiving or permissive as I am.<br>
<br>
Keep the peace.<br>
